snippet.title: Hawken Reborn - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
High-octane mech combat returns in Hawken Reborn, an all-new Free-to-Play PVE experience that brings the franchise’s unique flavor of visceral first-person shooter gameplay to Illal, a world riddled with warring factions and a gripping narrative.

Coming soon to PC Early Access on May 17, 2023. 

Learn more at www.HawkenReborn.com
